            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%235%E7%B1%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E8%82%A0%E6%81%AF%E8%82%89%E7%99%8C%E5%8F%98%23&amp;extparam=%235%E7%B1%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E5%BD%93%E5%BF%83%E8%82%A0%E6%81%AF%E8%82%89%E7%99%8C%E5%8F%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#5类人群当心肠息肉癌变#</span></a> 】专家表示，这5类人群当心肠道息肉癌变：①40岁以上有家族病史人群；②大肠腺瘤治疗后人群；③长期患有溃疡性结肠炎的患者；④接受过肠癌手术人群；⑤具有家族性腺瘤性息肉病或者是遗传性非息肉病的大肠癌家族史的直系亲属👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4992915077005342" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1gy1hm25hogx0fj21hc0u0tdq.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/MijlwnQalx08bVZzIPu0010412008Gz80E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706001426&amp;ssig=cRSkmIwhQG&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/eGd8vx6Rlx08bVZyrBzO010412004lXe0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706001426&amp;ssig=6FqcU9q3%2Bb&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Gc1g9FyDlx08bVZyroje010412002KhH0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;or