            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%8D%AB%E5%81%A5%E5%A7%94%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F%E8%AF%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%8D%AB%E5%81%A5%E5%A7%94%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F%E8%AF%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#国家卫健委要求加强出生证管理#</span></a>】国家卫生健康委日前印发通知，要求进一步加强出生医学证明等医疗文书管理工作。各医疗机构要①强化开具相关医疗文书的授权管理；②<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%90%91%E6%9C%AA%E5%B0%B1%E8%AF%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E5%BC%80%E5%85%B7%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E6%96%87%E4%B9%A6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%90%91%E6%9C%AA%E5%B0%B1%E8%AF%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E5%BC%80%E5%85%B7%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E6%96%87%E4%B9%A6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医疗机构不得向未就诊人员开具医疗文书#</span></a>；③不得在空白医疗文书上盖章；④加强废弃或空白医疗文书管理，及时回收销毁👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4992892851126314" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hm22xur2jvj61bu0qw1kx02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/eSrYOjAklx08bVTiTKQM01041200lvhu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706001426&amp;ssig=%2BM55PB1DP4&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/4CZu4eX4lx08bVTiYHbW01041200bhB90E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706001426&amp;ssig=lneOTkJk4M&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/tupxb66blx08bVTiASKk010412006Qv00E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1706001426&amp;ssig=Lp6cJNSJSE&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4992892851126314" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
