        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[疑问]#吃核桃能补脑是真的#真的！✅吃核桃有7个好处：补脑健脑、延缓衰老、缓解焦虑、守护血管健康、调节血糖、改善肠道菌群、改善睡眠质量。正常情况下，核桃...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E6%A0%B8%E6%A1%83%E8%83%BD%E8%A1%A5%E8%84%91%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E6%A0%B8%E6%A1%83%E8%83%BD%E8%A1%A5%E8%84%91%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃核桃能补脑是真的#</span></a><br><br>真的！✅<br><br>吃核桃有7个好处：补脑健脑、延缓衰老、缓解焦虑、守护血管健康、调节血糖、改善肠道菌群、改善睡眠质量。<br><br>正常情况下，核桃仁表面带有深褐色的核桃皮，口感有些苦涩。但如果想获得核桃中更多抗氧化成分，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%A0%B8%E6%A1%83%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%E5%B8%A6%E7%9A%AE%E5%90%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%A0%B8%E6%A1%83%E6%9C%80%E5%A5%BD%E5%B8%A6%E7%9A%AE%E5%90%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#核桃最好带皮吃#</span></a>。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>虽然坚果对预防肥胖有帮助，但也不能多吃。根据《中国居民膳食指南 (2022)》，建议每周吃50-70g坚果，相当于每天吃约1个大纸皮核桃或2-3个山核桃的量。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hm29e7f1pkg206g05xjxe.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
